# ─── OmanTaxi realtime (cross-device sync) ───────────────────────────────────
# Enables driver ↔ passenger sync across different devices via Ably pub/sub.
# Without this key the app still works, but only between tabs of the SAME browser.
#
# How to get a free key:
#   1. Create a free account at https://ably.com/
#   2. Open your app → "API Keys" tab.
#   3. Copy the key (format: "appId.keyId:keySecret"). The default key with
#      Publish + Subscribe + History capabilities is enough.
#   4. Paste it below into .env.local (NOT this example file).
#
# NOTE: This key ships to the browser (NEXT_PUBLIC_*). Use a key scoped to only
# Publish/Subscribe/History on the taxi channels — never your account secret.
NEXT_PUBLIC_ABLY_KEY=

# Optional: deploy under a sub-path (e.g. GitHub Pages project site).
# NEXT_PUBLIC_BASE_PATH=
